1
00:00:26,606 --> 00:00:30,201
we were returning from Shirdi and
our car broke down on the way...

2
00:00:30,377 --> 00:00:34,370
she is in labour,
can we come in for sometime?

3
00:00:34,548 --> 00:00:37,608
Call them in!
- Please come in!

4
00:00:53,233 --> 00:00:55,861
Thank you very much,
will I find a doctor here?

5
00:00:58,638 --> 00:01:00,572
So a baby is expected?
-Yes.

6
00:01:01,174 --> 00:01:02,801
Yourwife is expecting?
-Yes, doctor.

7
00:01:03,176 --> 00:01:05,576
Please hurry up!
-Yes, I am!

8
00:01:17,824 --> 00:01:21,191
Congratulations sir, God has given
you a very pretty daughter!

9
00:01:21,328 --> 00:01:23,592
How is Rama?
- She is perfectly alright.

10
00:01:23,697 --> 00:01:25,255
She has just fallen asleep.

11
00:01:27,601 --> 00:01:29,193
Here you are!

12
00:01:30,203 --> 00:01:33,195
Great! She was born even before
I could get here.

13
00:01:33,373 --> 00:01:36,365
Doctor, please don't get upset
at my daughter's haste.

14
00:01:36,610 --> 00:01:39,602
Thanks for the trouble
you took to come here.

15
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:42,610
Here is your fees.
-What is the need for this?

16
00:01:43,216 --> 00:01:44,376
Actually I need it!

17
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:50,618
Aunt Leela, the medicine you gave
me for a cold, really worked.

18
00:01:51,391 --> 00:01:55,225
Doctor, you've taken fees to come
here.

19
00:01:57,230 --> 00:01:59,221
Do you also collect to leave?
Okay, I am leaving!

20
00:02:07,774 --> 00:02:09,173
Please take this money.

21
00:02:09,309 --> 00:02:14,872
Sir, we may be poor but we can't
accept this. Please keep it back.

22
00:02:15,382 --> 00:02:17,782
Then you tell me,
what can I do for you?

23
00:02:18,218 --> 00:02:20,686
Sir, we don't have a child...

24
00:02:21,188 --> 00:02:24,851
please pray that
we also get a child...

25
00:02:25,358 --> 00:02:28,657
actually, a child was born
in our house last night...

26
00:02:28,895 --> 00:02:32,194
what I mean is that
even my wife should...

27
00:02:32,466 --> 00:02:35,867
He has understood!
-Yes, I will surely pray for you.

28
00:02:36,603 --> 00:02:42,200
You'll have done us a big favor,
if we would get twin daughters...

29
00:02:42,542 --> 00:02:44,806
then I would surely give you
one of my daughters.

30
00:02:45,545 --> 00:02:48,810
Okay, good bye!
- Good bye, sir.

31
00:02:58,225 --> 00:02:59,817
Listen, come here...

32
00:03:06,433 --> 00:03:09,766
Why did you do this?
- They really did get twin daughters.

33
00:03:10,170 --> 00:03:12,161
So you hid one of them?
- So what?

34
00:03:12,606 --> 00:03:14,767
What would they do with
two identical daughters?

35
00:03:15,175 --> 00:03:18,611
Didn't he say that if they would
get twins, he'd give us one!

36
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:24,875
He said it that doesn't mean he'd
do it, even I say a lot of things!

37
00:03:26,186 --> 00:03:33,615
Why didn't you think how we'll
raise a child from a rich family?

38
00:03:35,262 --> 00:03:42,191
We'll give her the love that is
rarely found in the rich families!

39
00:06:50,557 --> 00:06:52,752
Grandmother, your
cough has increased.

40
00:06:53,526 --> 00:06:57,519
Yes child but yet, I don't die!

41
00:06:58,264 --> 00:07:00,198
Grandmother, have this medicine.

42
00:07:09,876 --> 00:07:13,141
I am losing my eyesight too!

43
00:07:14,314 --> 00:07:18,717
But I don't mind because,
I cannot see...

44
00:07:19,152 --> 00:07:21,518
the torture that is meted
out on you.

45
00:07:23,323 --> 00:07:24,654
Wretched girl!

46
00:07:25,592 --> 00:07:29,722
Even the servants are not
called like this!

47
00:07:30,163 --> 00:07:32,154
You go, child.
- But grandmother...

48
00:07:32,499 --> 00:07:36,162
Are you dead?
- Go child, don't bother about me.

49
00:07:45,645 --> 00:07:46,634
Yes, aunty.

50
00:07:46,813 --> 00:07:50,874
I've been calling you since past
two hours. Couldn't you hear me?

51
00:07:52,652 --> 00:07:55,849
Aunty, grandmother...
- Damn that old woman!

52
00:07:56,256 --> 00:07:57,848
We'll be relieved if she dies!

53
00:07:58,191 --> 00:08:00,853
I feel like conducting her
final rites when she is alive!

54
00:08:02,362 --> 00:08:07,459
Stop staring! Will you get me hot
water or will your ancestors get it?

55
00:08:07,834 --> 00:08:09,734
I'll get it.

56
00:08:10,570 --> 00:08:13,130
Will your legs break
if you walk faster?

57
00:08:37,163 --> 00:08:39,757
I've not seen
a bigger idiot than you!

58
00:08:40,166 --> 00:08:43,158
It's time for my college and
you've not yet ironed my sari?

59
00:08:43,503 --> 00:08:45,664
I'll do it, Sheila.
- Hurry up, stupid!

60
00:08:58,184 --> 00:08:59,845
Did you get the soap?
- I'll get it.

61
00:09:00,186 --> 00:09:04,350
Wonderwhy she is with us!

62
00:09:04,691 --> 00:09:07,592
She will never do anything
unless you don't tell her.

63
00:09:07,927 --> 00:09:12,193
Why don't you tell her anything?

64
00:09:12,465 --> 00:09:14,399
Wait a minute!

65
00:09:15,201 --> 00:09:17,692
And what are you doing there?

66
00:09:19,205 --> 00:09:21,799
I was just polishing my shoes!

67
00:09:22,275 --> 00:09:26,211
Have you worked all your life
that today you are doing this?

68
00:09:26,746 --> 00:09:28,475
Hey, wretched girl!
Polish these shoes.

69
00:09:28,815 --> 00:09:30,806
But...
- Give it to her.

70
00:09:31,317 --> 00:09:32,545
Giving!

71
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:36,652
Here, child.
- Polish them quickly.

72
00:09:37,323 --> 00:09:39,814
Why did you ask her to do it, the
poor girl does many other things.

73
00:09:40,226 --> 00:09:43,753
Do you ever see how much
she eats the whole day?

74
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:46,755
If she does some exercise,
her fat will burn out!

75
00:09:47,233 --> 00:09:50,794
She gets hot water for you everyday,
why don't you repair the geyser?

76
00:09:51,371 --> 00:09:54,966
I'll do that only when the lawyer
will get this month's allowance.

77
00:09:55,575 --> 00:09:58,840
Didn't Seeta's father trust
you even a bit...

78
00:09:59,245 --> 00:10:02,180
why did he entrust the entire
property to the lawyers before dying?

79
00:10:02,548 --> 00:10:05,176
This bungalow is also in Seeta's
name and what do we get?

80
00:10:05,518 --> 00:10:07,452
All we get is
Rs. 5,000/- per month.

81
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:09,611
That too we'll get only till
Seeta gets married.

82
00:10:09,889 --> 00:10:11,481
Her marriage!

83
00:10:13,192 --> 00:10:16,719
It's a chiffon sari,
do you know how expensive it is?

84
00:10:17,263 --> 00:10:19,197
Be careful while ironing it.

85
00:10:24,203 --> 00:10:27,195
What is it?
- Sir, your tea.

86
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:31,198
Old man, who asked you
to get tea for me?

87
00:10:32,412 --> 00:10:34,676
Where is that pretty girl?

88
00:10:35,315 --> 00:10:39,775
You mean Seeta, she is
attending to Madam's chores.

89
00:10:40,653 --> 00:10:43,781
ldiot, anybody can attend
to sister's chores...

90
00:10:44,223 --> 00:10:46,623
ask her to attend to me,
give me a match!

91
00:10:50,897 --> 00:10:54,890
Listen, I don't want to see
your mug from tomorrow morning.

92
00:10:55,301 --> 00:10:56,825
Get out now!

93
00:10:57,403 --> 00:10:59,803
Sister, can l
polish father's shoes?

94
00:11:00,239 --> 00:11:01,968
No Babloo, I will do it,
give it here!

95
00:11:02,275 --> 00:11:06,837
No, while you iron this sari,
I'll polish these shoes.

96
00:11:07,180 --> 00:11:10,672
Both the jobs will be done soon!
-And what if your mother sees?

97
00:11:10,917 --> 00:11:12,407
She'll scold me.

98
00:11:12,518 --> 00:11:14,850
And if you are late,
she will yet scold you!

99
00:11:15,188 --> 00:11:18,851
Alright, do it but
don't dirty your hands.

100
00:11:19,692 --> 00:11:23,526
Seeta, are you going to get the
soap or shall I come and hit you?

101
00:11:23,863 --> 00:11:26,730
Oh my, I forgot!
I'll get it, aunty!

102
00:11:33,206 --> 00:11:36,698
What took you so long
to get a bar of soap?

103
00:11:37,210 --> 00:11:38,871
Get out from here!

104
00:11:45,952 --> 00:11:47,886
Yes.
- Please come here.

105
00:11:48,221 --> 00:11:53,625
I have a lot of work.
-Will you stand there and talk to me?

106
00:11:57,730 --> 00:12:02,497
I won't eat you up, why don't you
do things for me too?

107
00:12:03,503 --> 00:12:06,336
Will you do it?
-What do you want me to do?

108
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:10,166
You are very simple! Okay,
can you stitch up this button?

109
00:12:11,277 --> 00:12:13,768
You keep it aside,
I'll do it in the afternoon.

110
00:12:14,180 --> 00:12:16,171
It will take two minutes, do it now.

111
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:19,441
Here is the needle and
thread and the button too!

112
00:12:23,823 --> 00:12:29,193
I mean it, Seeta. I feel very sorry
to see you in this state.

113
00:12:29,662 --> 00:12:34,463
But you are to be blamed for this,
just trust me once...

114
00:12:34,801 --> 00:12:38,794
nobody will tell you a word but
you think that I am your enemy!

115
00:12:41,974 --> 00:12:43,942
Look what she has done!
-What happened?

116
00:12:46,212 --> 00:12:49,875
Coming!
- Sheila, please forgive me.

117
00:12:51,784 --> 00:12:53,775
What happened, child?

118
00:12:54,220 --> 00:12:57,678
Aunty, I am extremely sorry, there
were too many things at a time...

119
00:12:58,024 --> 00:13:01,482
Liar! Mother, she burnt my sari!

120
00:13:01,861 --> 00:13:04,830
You louse! How dare you?

121
00:13:06,232 --> 00:13:08,757
It happened by mistake.
- It was by mistake...

122
00:13:08,935 --> 00:13:10,926
or you did it purposely?
You are jealous of my daughter!

123
00:13:11,537 --> 00:13:14,165
Why would I be jealous ofher?
- How dare you argue?

124
00:13:15,174 --> 00:13:17,540
I will skin your hide!
-Aunty!

125
00:13:17,844 --> 00:13:19,835
Don't beat her!
- Forgive me, aunty.

126
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:24,181
I will kill you today!
Stop interfering, move away!

127
00:13:33,993 --> 00:13:37,690
Get inside! Only when you'll be
locked in here, will you realize.

128
00:13:38,197 --> 00:13:41,189
Only when you'll not be fed for
4-5 days you'll value things.

129
00:13:43,669 --> 00:13:46,194
You keep quiet, you've spoilt her!

130
00:14:00,219 --> 00:14:06,317
Mother, father,
why did you'll leave me?

131
00:14:08,828 --> 00:14:11,490
Nobody loves me here!

132
00:14:12,832 --> 00:14:19,328
Mother, I would like to come to you!

133
00:14:33,186 --> 00:14:36,519
Listen to me, for how long
will you order food from outside?

134
00:14:36,856 --> 00:14:39,620
Please let Seeta out.
- Stop siding her!

135
00:14:39,959 --> 00:14:41,517
I just suggested.

136
00:14:41,627 --> 00:14:43,788
She has become too big for her
boots.

137
00:14:44,197 --> 00:14:46,722
Two days if she is inside,
she'll get back into her senses!

138
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:49,760
That's okay but...
- But what?

139
00:14:50,203 --> 00:14:51,397
Nothing!

140
00:14:52,305 --> 00:14:54,296
Mother, the laundry man hasn't
got my blue sari yet.

141
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:58,533
I've to go to college.
- Do you have dearth of saris?

142
00:14:59,879 --> 00:15:02,143
I promised my friends that
I would wear a blue sari today.

143
00:15:02,548 --> 00:15:06,575
That laundry man is very mean!
- I am a little surprised, child.

144
00:15:07,153 --> 00:15:11,613
Do you go to college to study or
display your sari to your friends?

145
00:15:11,958 --> 00:15:13,858
Shut up, you are
always taunting her!

146
00:15:14,227 --> 00:15:19,164
This is the age to flaunt things.
Child, you sit at home today.

147
00:15:21,167 --> 00:15:24,830
I've to pay my college fees today.
- Fees??

148
00:15:25,705 --> 00:15:31,644
Is it the 1st today?
- I think so!

149
00:15:32,178 --> 00:15:36,171
Then the lawyer will come today.
- If it's the 1st, he'll surely come.

150
00:15:36,682 --> 00:15:38,946
Please come in, Mr. Gupta.

151
00:15:40,987 --> 00:15:42,852
What is the matter,
you don't look alright.

152
00:15:43,189 --> 00:15:44,884
Nothing much, I've got cold,
you please sit!

153
00:15:45,191 --> 00:15:48,456
You should have called a doctor.
- Ramu, get tea and snacks quickly!

154
00:15:48,628 --> 00:15:50,619
Hello!
- Hello!

155
00:15:50,997 --> 00:15:54,626
There is no need to call for
anything. I am in a hurry, please call Seeta.

156
00:15:54,967 --> 00:16:00,564
You come here as ifit's a duty.
-Well, it is a duty.

157
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:04,132
Your brother made me the trustee
ofhis entire wealth.

158
00:16:04,644 --> 00:16:08,478
But the responsibility of such
a vast wealth is not at all easy.

159
00:16:08,814 --> 00:16:11,647
Mr. Gupta, you have not
seen our responsibility.

160
00:16:12,151 --> 00:16:15,143
We have raised this orphan girl
as our own child.

161
00:16:15,488 --> 00:16:20,152
We always have the fear that people
may criticize our upbringing.

162
00:16:20,493 --> 00:16:23,758
You do take care ofher!
- But yet, I live under that fear.

163
00:16:24,163 --> 00:16:25,892
I don't want to lack anything
in my responsibility.

164
00:16:26,232 --> 00:16:29,668
I suggest that you get her married.

165
00:16:30,169 --> 00:16:32,831
Your responsibility will end
and so will mine!

166
00:16:33,272 --> 00:16:38,175
As per brother's will, our
responsibly is till her marriage.

167
00:16:38,611 --> 00:16:40,602
Have you'll seen
any suitable boy for her?

168
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:43,644
We've seen dozens of them!

169
00:16:44,183 --> 00:16:49,678
But I feel that not a single one
is suitable for our Seeta.

170
00:16:50,189 --> 00:16:53,590
Mr. Gupta, why don't you
suggest some good proposal?

171
00:16:53,859 --> 00:16:57,192
Isn't it, Kaushalya?
-Yes, even we will keep looking!

172
00:16:57,530 --> 00:16:59,691
Yes, I will look out.

173
00:17:00,566 --> 00:17:02,134
Come, child!

174
00:17:02,134 --> 00:17:04,602
Why did you get it, you should have
asked the servant to get it.

175
00:17:04,870 --> 00:17:08,567
I'll make the tea. She loves
doing household chores.

176
00:17:09,141 --> 00:17:14,135
Even if I stop her, she keeps
doing something or the other!

177
00:17:15,147 --> 00:17:18,480
That's very nice, girls must be
well versed with domestic chores.

178
00:17:19,352 --> 00:17:22,480
How are you, child?
-Yes, thank you.

179
00:17:26,559 --> 00:17:29,494
Child, this is your
monthly allowance.

180
00:17:30,162 --> 00:17:33,154
Take it!
- Count it!

181
00:17:33,499 --> 00:17:35,763
What is the need for that,
it must be exact!

182
00:17:36,168 --> 00:17:41,606
I will be convinced.
- Child, give the money to your uncle.

183
00:17:43,976 --> 00:17:45,967
Here, take your tea.
- Thank you.

184
00:17:55,187 --> 00:17:57,178
It's exact, Mr. Gupta.
- It had to be!

185
00:17:57,523 --> 00:17:59,514
He was just joking about it!

186
00:18:00,226 --> 00:18:02,694
Don't give me, give it
to the person it belongs to.

187
00:18:04,797 --> 00:18:06,788
Alright Mr. Badrinath,
permit me to leave.

188
00:18:07,133 --> 00:18:11,797
Have some more tea.
- Let him leave, he is a busy man!

189
00:18:12,371 --> 00:18:15,135
She's right, I am in a hurry.
Good bye!

190
00:18:21,814 --> 00:18:24,544
What are you doing here?
Come on, take this tray inside.

191
00:18:30,556 --> 00:18:33,719
You seem to be in a great hurry
to get your niece married.

192
00:18:34,226 --> 00:18:40,495
Don't you know the day she gets
married, you'll be out on the street!

193
00:18:41,167 --> 00:18:45,501
That's right but...
- Damn you and your buts!!

194
00:18:45,838 --> 00:18:47,829
That too is right!

195
00:18:53,212 --> 00:18:56,511
Yes, grandmother.
- Come here, child.

196
00:19:04,190 --> 00:19:06,181
Sit close to me.

197
00:19:11,897 --> 00:19:13,888
You are looking very beautiful.

198
00:19:15,301 --> 00:19:17,565
You look like a princess!

199
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:24,869
You mark my words, one day a
prince in a shining armor will come...

200
00:19:27,213 --> 00:19:31,206
and will sweep away my princess
and take her to his kingdom!

201
00:19:34,286 --> 00:19:38,723
These are mere fairy tales,
no prince will ever come!

202
00:19:39,225 --> 00:19:42,558
He will, my child. I have
a strong feeling that he will come!

203
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:47,222
Grandmother, you are very nice!

204
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:53,238
Grandmother, I am going!

205
00:19:57,243 --> 00:19:58,232
Aunty, you called.

206
00:19:58,310 --> 00:20:00,676
Yes, why are you yet
dressed like this?

207
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:08,177
Remove the jewellery and this sari!
Don't you feel like taking them out?

208
00:20:08,587 --> 00:20:11,522
Give it soon and
what about this sari?

209
00:20:12,191 --> 00:20:16,855
I'll go in my room and take it out.
-Why there? Take it out here!

210
00:20:21,567 --> 00:20:24,798
Stop this act of a chastity,
shameless girl!!

211
00:20:25,437 --> 00:20:29,203
Take it out and
go and cook the food!

212
00:20:30,209 --> 00:20:32,803
Aunty, how can l...
-What do you mean?

213
00:20:33,312 --> 00:20:35,212
Are you going or shall I hit you?

214
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:43,354
Oh! So my sister did manage
to take out your clothes?

215
00:20:44,423 --> 00:20:47,881
Why have you left the rest,
do they belong to you?

216
00:20:50,563 --> 00:20:53,555
What is it, old man?
-You had asked for cigarettes.

217
00:20:53,899 --> 00:20:55,890
Throw them for all I care!

218
00:20:56,235 --> 00:21:01,605
Grandmother!!
- Stop crying, my child!!

219
00:21:02,174 --> 00:21:06,702
Why can't I die?
- Don't say that, my child!

220
00:21:08,514 --> 00:21:11,574
Grandmother...
- Don't say a word, child.

221
00:21:11,884 --> 00:21:13,875
I understand your tears!

222
00:21:15,287 --> 00:21:22,523
God, isn't there anybody in this
world who can save her from them?

223
00:21:59,398 --> 00:22:03,494
''Life's a game,
some win, some lose...''

224
00:22:03,936 --> 00:22:08,168
''there are experts,
and there are novices''

225
00:22:10,442 --> 00:22:14,742
''Do you get it, mister...?
Or perhaps you, fatso?''

226
00:22:15,381 --> 00:22:19,181
''There are experts
and there are novices''

227
00:22:20,319 --> 00:22:24,187
''Life's a game.
Some win, some lose...''

228
00:22:24,690 --> 00:22:28,854
''there are experts,
and there are novices''

229
00:22:30,996 --> 00:22:35,729
''Do you get it mister...?
Or maybe you have?

230
00:23:16,975 --> 00:23:20,240
''Cut the nonsense.
Get to work, Raka''

231
00:23:20,879 --> 00:23:25,714
''Oh yes, it's work that
will bring you fame''

232
00:23:35,194 --> 00:23:39,790
''You're like a bird in flight,
I swear by you''

233
00:23:40,265 --> 00:23:43,723
''Don't you fall...
watch your step''

234
00:23:44,203 --> 00:23:48,663
''Get that, mister...?
Or perhaps you, sister?''

235
00:24:34,953 --> 00:24:36,944
''Step back, children...
- Sit down''

236
00:24:37,289 --> 00:24:40,452
''Turn around, snobbish one''

237
00:24:41,727 --> 00:24:44,457
''And people will give you
a round of applause''

238
00:24:44,696 --> 00:24:46,186
''Applause!''

239
00:24:55,874 --> 00:25:00,208
''A true spectacle
I will show them...''

240
00:25:00,445 --> 00:25:03,676
''every heart, I will send pounding''

241
00:25:04,149 --> 00:25:08,643
''Get that, sardarji?
Get it, lady?''

242
00:25:09,154 --> 00:25:13,147
''There are experts
and there are novices''

243
00:25:18,263 --> 00:25:22,324
''Life's a game.
Some win, some lose.

244
00:25:22,668 --> 00:25:26,934
''There are experts
and there are novices''

245
00:25:29,408 --> 00:25:33,606
''Got it, mister?
- Or you, Pathan?''

246
00:25:57,002 --> 00:25:58,799
Damn it!
-What is the matter, chief?.

247
00:25:59,204 --> 00:26:01,138
Nothing Cheena,
it's just my bad luck.

248
00:26:01,406 --> 00:26:05,137
I bet on the wrong number.
- But you were given a right tip!

249
00:26:05,644 --> 00:26:08,135
I saw number six last night
in my dream and I bet on that number.

250
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:10,380
And now I've lost the money!

251
00:26:12,150 --> 00:26:13,845
What do you think will be the
number today?

252
00:26:14,152 --> 00:26:15,642
Ace!

253
00:26:16,154 --> 00:26:17,815
Are you sure?
-Yes, I am!

254
00:26:18,156 --> 00:26:20,488
I've neverwon the way you do!

255
00:26:21,226 --> 00:26:26,493
Come on, take your share.
- Geeta, you've made an equal share.

256
00:26:26,765 --> 00:26:29,495
Raka, you can play five times today.

257
00:26:29,768 --> 00:26:33,169
What about the notes
that are under yourfeet?

258
00:26:33,505 --> 00:26:34,836
What do you mean?

259
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:37,231
Move your leg and
give me that money!

260
00:26:38,176 --> 00:26:43,170
Oh, these? Don't shout,
I did not hide them purposely.

261
00:26:43,582 --> 00:26:49,748
You do it everyday but when I get
angry, you'll realise it!

262
00:26:50,188 --> 00:26:55,524
Just try doing that,
don't forget my name is Geeta!

263
00:26:55,861 --> 00:26:58,659
Even my name is Raka,
I'll break your legs!

264
00:26:58,997 --> 00:27:01,124
What did you say?
Do you think you are a don?

265
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:04,125
How dare you show me that knife?
- Leave her, chief!

266
00:27:05,137 --> 00:27:08,573
You steal and then you show
this knife? Apologize to him!

267
00:27:09,141 --> 00:27:13,475
I don't want to work with her, does
she think we cannot do without her?

268
00:27:14,146 --> 00:27:18,139
No, the public throws money when
you show your juggling tricks!

269
00:27:22,254 --> 00:27:26,554
Such things happen chief,
why make it a big issue?

270
00:27:26,892 --> 00:27:28,883
Nonsense! How could she
threaten me?

271
00:27:29,261 --> 00:27:31,752
It was just a knife!

272
00:27:32,264 --> 00:27:36,166
Go to your room and rest.
-You don't side her!

273
00:27:41,173 --> 00:27:44,165
You are back, Geeta.
- Mother, I am very hungry.

274
00:27:44,343 --> 00:27:47,506
You will drop the tray,
come with me to the temple.

275
00:27:47,779 --> 00:27:49,770
You go there, I'll go home
and eat something.

276
00:27:50,182 --> 00:27:53,515
I haven't cooked,
I'll come back and make something.

277
00:27:54,286 --> 00:27:57,187
I'll be famished by then!
- It doesn't take long to cook.

278
00:27:57,622 --> 00:27:59,681
I'll be back soon.
- I'll knead the dough meanwhile.

279
00:27:59,858 --> 00:28:03,521
No, you please don't touch
anything in the kitchen.

280
00:28:04,229 --> 00:28:05,821
I'll come back soon.

281
00:28:07,532 --> 00:28:11,127
Geeta, why are you straining
your eyes in the night?

282
00:28:14,172 --> 00:28:18,131
Cheena told me that today,
you fought with Raka again.

283
00:28:19,144 --> 00:28:23,547
We do it everyday but actually,
it was my fault.

284
00:28:24,282 --> 00:28:28,150
Stop fighting with the poor boy,
think of your future.

285
00:28:28,687 --> 00:28:32,555
I may not live long,
I suggest you hold his hand.

286
00:28:34,159 --> 00:28:37,253
But why should I hold Raka's hand?

287
00:28:37,696 --> 00:28:41,154
You fool, I am talking
about your marriage!

288
00:28:41,500 --> 00:28:46,631
You mean with Raka?
-Why, what does he lack?

289
00:28:46,938 --> 00:28:49,930
He may be a little hot tempered
but he has a clear heart!

290
00:28:50,609 --> 00:28:53,169
Mother, you are getting senile!

291
00:28:53,478 --> 00:28:56,413
Yes, I have!
It's a sin to talk to you.

292
00:28:58,183 --> 00:29:01,175
What is it?
- The bride groom is coming!

293
00:29:24,209 --> 00:29:27,736
Did you see, he is a drunkard,
can I marry such a man?

294
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:30,976
No, a prince will come here
to marry you.

295
00:29:31,483 --> 00:29:36,216
Yes, a prince in a shining armor
will come to marry me.

296
00:29:41,927 --> 00:29:44,225
Have you seen this stick,
how light it!

297
00:29:46,031 --> 00:29:49,489
Along with a medical degree from
London, I've got this golf stick too!

298
00:29:51,803 --> 00:29:59,574
I've seen that men often get a
foreign wife when they go abroad.

299
00:30:01,847 --> 00:30:03,747
That is their problem!

300
00:30:04,216 --> 00:30:06,844
I don't say that women
out there are not good...

301
00:30:09,521 --> 00:30:14,720
there's a big difference in our
culture & marriage is impossible!

302
00:30:18,396 --> 00:30:21,763
What is your image of an ideal wife?

303
00:30:23,268 --> 00:30:27,204
A sari clad girl, who cooks well...

304
00:30:27,539 --> 00:30:29,530
a very simple, Indian woman!

305
00:30:29,808 --> 00:30:34,211
He'll surely like her, Seeta is the
kind of girl Dr. Ravi is looking for!

306
00:30:34,546 --> 00:30:37,538
What kind of girl does
that damn doctorwant?

307
00:30:38,216 --> 00:30:42,744
A very simple Indian girl,
just like our Seeta.

308
00:30:43,221 --> 00:30:48,215
Is that so?

309
00:31:05,610 --> 00:31:07,168
Come, child.

310
00:31:08,313 --> 00:31:12,511
God bless you! Is she the one?
- No, she is my daughter, Sheila.

311
00:31:13,185 --> 00:31:14,777
She is doing her B.A.

312
00:31:15,187 --> 00:31:18,850
Mother, can I get some tea or
coffee? -No child, Ramu will get it.

313
00:31:19,224 --> 00:31:21,317
She is very fond of
doing domestic chores.

314
00:31:21,526 --> 00:31:24,518
She doesn't have any habits
of a modern girl.

315
00:31:25,530 --> 00:31:27,862
Child, why didn't you
get Seeta along?

316
00:31:28,300 --> 00:31:30,734
She's in her room...
- I'll go and get her.

317
00:31:31,203 --> 00:31:33,194
You talk to aunty,
I'll be right back!

318
00:31:35,207 --> 00:31:38,540
Ramu, how does the boy look?

319
00:31:39,211 --> 00:31:41,805
You must have seen him.
- He looks very decent.

320
00:31:42,314 --> 00:31:47,342
He'll make a good husband for
Seeta. - Listen, what is his name?

321
00:31:47,586 --> 00:31:53,218
Ravi, why are you so quiet?
-What should I say?

322
00:31:53,558 --> 00:31:58,552
Talk as much as you want, after
your marriage, you won't get that chance!

323
00:31:59,231 --> 00:32:00,823
Isn't it, Mr. Badrinath?

324
00:32:21,253 --> 00:32:23,778
Walk down or I will...
-Aunty!!

325
00:32:47,212 --> 00:32:48,804
Sit here, child!

326
00:32:56,021 --> 00:32:57,488
Sit down!

327
00:33:16,341 --> 00:33:18,502
Is she Seeta?
-Yes!

328
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:24,171
Mr. Gupta told us something else!

329
00:33:24,449 --> 00:33:26,713
He speaks about the 18 century...

330
00:33:27,185 --> 00:33:30,518
if these girls will not be
fashionable then will we be?

331
00:33:30,855 --> 00:33:34,188
Besides, this is the age
of progress, isn't it Ravi?

332
00:33:36,261 --> 00:33:41,699
Right, I think our country has
progressed more than the west!

333
00:33:43,201 --> 00:33:47,194
They would like to have tea
made by you, go get it.

334
00:33:48,540 --> 00:33:49,529
Go!!

335
00:33:56,581 --> 00:33:58,572
Ramu, give the tray to Seeta.

336
00:34:24,576 --> 00:34:27,170
How did you fall,
what is the matter?

337
00:34:28,613 --> 00:34:31,776
Did you hurt yourself?. I am sorry,
your clothes are stained.

338
00:34:32,183 --> 00:34:33,582
Let's leave, son!

339
00:34:34,185 --> 00:34:39,589
Please don't leave.
- No, it's quite late.

340
00:34:39,891 --> 00:34:42,189
We'll come some other time,
let's go Ravi.

341
00:34:42,861 --> 00:34:44,726
But Mr. Chaudhary...
- Let's go!

342
00:34:45,997 --> 00:34:53,199
Please wait Mr. Chaudhary,
please listen to me...

343
00:34:56,541 --> 00:35:00,204
Please don't insult us and go.

344
00:35:01,146 --> 00:35:06,311
I assure you that you what you are
seeing is absolutely wrong!

345
00:35:07,152 --> 00:35:10,815
My Seeta is not like that, she
will serve you whole heartedly.

346
00:35:12,157 --> 00:35:17,561
For God's sake, please stop.
-What can I do?

347
00:35:18,163 --> 00:35:20,654
Ravi, please accept this proposal.

348
00:35:21,666 --> 00:35:26,899
Well, l...
- I plead to you, son.

349
00:35:27,305 --> 00:35:30,832
No grandmother, please stop it!

350
00:35:58,570 --> 00:36:02,131
Kaushalya, whatever you are doing
is not right!

351
00:37:12,810 --> 00:37:15,643
You?!
-Who else could it be?

352
00:37:16,614 --> 00:37:21,745
I am the only one who writhes
in pain when I see your sorrows!

353
00:37:22,820 --> 00:37:25,584
But don't worry, if not Ravi,
I am still there!

354
00:37:25,924 --> 00:37:27,915
You can find better boys!

355
00:37:28,927 --> 00:37:31,521
Ranjit, you please go from here.

356
00:37:31,829 --> 00:37:37,597
You are great! You want to
mourn for a stranger...

357
00:37:38,603 --> 00:37:42,266
and the ones who are crazy about
you, you don't even look at them!

358
00:37:43,808 --> 00:37:46,743
You please go or else...
- Or else what?

359
00:37:47,178 --> 00:37:50,614
I will scream.
- If you scream you will be defamed.

360
00:37:51,182 --> 00:37:54,174
Please go away!
- Scream, I will not go!!

361
00:37:54,852 --> 00:37:56,376
Grandmother!

362
00:37:59,524 --> 00:38:00,456
Uncle!

363
00:38:06,130 --> 00:38:07,791
What happened?

364
00:38:22,847 --> 00:38:25,611
Tell me, where is my wallet, thief?.

365
00:38:26,150 --> 00:38:28,141
Where is the thief?.
- In front of you!

366
00:38:28,586 --> 00:38:30,144
Aunty, he is lying.

367
00:38:30,288 --> 00:38:32,153
Shut up! Talk when I ask you to talk!

368
00:38:32,290 --> 00:38:34,815
What is the matter, Ranjit?
- She cleaned my room today.

369
00:38:35,159 --> 00:38:37,150
After that my wallet was missing,
who else could have taken it?

370
00:38:37,295 --> 00:38:40,287
You wretched, horrible girl,
you've started stealing too?

371
00:38:42,166 --> 00:38:45,602
Uncle, I have not stolen anything.

372
00:38:46,437 --> 00:38:52,433
You can search my room.
-Yes, you can check her room.

373
00:38:52,810 --> 00:38:55,244
Yes sister, let's both
search her room.

374
00:39:11,195 --> 00:39:12,856
Here it is!

375
00:39:15,199 --> 00:39:20,398
Detestable girl! You steal and
then you make false promises!

376
00:39:21,205 --> 00:39:26,541
Sister, you move away, your
thrashing will not affect her.

377
00:39:30,214 --> 00:39:32,546
You thief! I will skin your hide!

378
00:39:38,222 --> 00:39:40,554
Someone please save her!

379
00:39:44,762 --> 00:39:46,753
Please don't hit her!

380
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,893
For God's sake, please stop!

381
00:39:55,239 --> 00:39:56,706
Stop, Ranjit!!

382
00:39:58,042 --> 00:40:01,170
Grandmother, please save me!

383
00:40:02,180 --> 00:40:04,671
This old woman will save you?

384
00:40:05,183 --> 00:40:11,179
Grandmother, please save me!
- Ranjit, let her go, I plead to you.

385
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:14,784
Then tell her to stay
within her limits...

386
00:40:15,259 --> 00:40:17,591
or else I will skin her hide!

387
00:40:24,202 --> 00:40:28,195
Grandmother!
- Stop crying, child!

388
00:41:01,873 --> 00:41:03,773
Where are you?

389
00:41:04,175 --> 00:41:06,166
Oh! You are here!

390
00:41:06,577 --> 00:41:08,772
What happened?
-Ask what did not happen?

391
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:11,171
Do you know what your niece has
done?

392
00:41:11,616 --> 00:41:16,246
What did she do now?
-What can she do, she has run away!

393
00:41:20,191 --> 00:41:22,182
Seeta has run away?!
- Oh God, what will we do now?

394
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:25,552
What will we tell people,
we have been defamed!

395
00:41:25,863 --> 00:41:27,854
You are more concerned
about the allowance.

396
00:41:28,466 --> 00:41:30,798
The way you'll were behaving
with her, she had to run away!

397
00:41:31,202 --> 00:41:33,693
Will you just lecture me
or even do something?

398
00:41:34,205 --> 00:41:37,538
We should do something
but what should I do?

399
00:41:37,875 --> 00:41:41,709
Look for her, report
the matter to the police.

400
00:41:42,213 --> 00:41:45,546
That's right!
- Leave this now!

401
00:41:46,217 --> 00:41:48,811
I did not like her
behaviour these days.

402
00:41:49,353 --> 00:41:51,753
She was acting too big
for her shoes!

403
00:41:52,223 --> 00:41:55,886
Why Ranjit had to go to Delhi this
morning? Did you get the number?

404
00:42:00,498 --> 00:42:08,166
I am Badrinath speaking.
Actually, my niece...

405
00:42:08,673 --> 00:42:16,170
Seeta, has left the house!

406
00:42:17,181 --> 00:42:19,172
And we are very worried about her.

407
00:42:20,184 --> 00:42:22,175
What, why did she go away?

408
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:29,182
Actually, her mental state is...

409
00:42:30,595 --> 00:42:33,530
You come to the police station,
I'll write down your report.

410
00:42:33,931 --> 00:42:35,922
And yes, do get her photograph.

411
00:42:40,538 --> 00:42:43,371
What will we do if we don't find her?

412
00:42:43,774 --> 00:42:46,299
That wretched Gupta will not
give us a penny!

413
00:42:47,812 --> 00:42:50,645
O God, please have mercy on us!

414
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:58,718
Aunty, what have you cooked
today?

415
00:42:59,223 --> 00:43:02,659
The stove has become cold but
I wonder where Geeta is!

416
00:43:03,194 --> 00:43:05,662
I wonder if she has gone to buy
vegetables or grow them!

417
00:43:06,264 --> 00:43:11,566
She has gone to buy vegetables! In
that case you observe a fast today.

418
00:43:12,169 --> 00:43:14,569
She is playing marbles
with the children of the area.

419
00:43:15,306 --> 00:43:19,709
What, I have been waiting for her
and she's playing marbles?

420
00:43:20,278 --> 00:43:22,838
Are you saying the truth?
- I've seen it with my own eyes!

421
00:43:23,648 --> 00:43:28,176
Don't mind but it doesn't look good
if a young girl plays with marbles.

422
00:43:28,552 --> 00:43:30,315
I will go and break her bones!

423
00:43:30,521 --> 00:43:34,184
Aunty!
- Give it to me!

424
00:43:41,198 --> 00:43:43,462
Her marbles are very lucky,
she always wins!

425
00:43:43,634 --> 00:43:45,625
Are your marbles over?

426
00:43:45,970 --> 00:43:48,530
Here, play with them.
- Give it to me!

427
00:43:52,643 --> 00:43:54,873
Now tell me which one should I aim?
- The green one!

428
00:43:56,480 --> 00:43:58,471
You are cheating,
you're crossing the line!

429
00:43:58,716 --> 00:44:01,150
What did you say?

430
00:44:01,485 --> 00:44:05,148
Don't waste time, hurry up!
- I get angry if someone provokes me!

431
00:44:05,489 --> 00:44:07,480
Shall I aim the green one?
-Yes.

432
00:44:09,760 --> 00:44:12,490
What are you doing here?
- I was just playing!

433
00:44:14,165 --> 00:44:17,760
You've been missing
since past 2 hours.

434
00:44:18,169 --> 00:44:19,500
Why are you hitting me?

435
00:44:19,670 --> 00:44:22,605
Do you want me to love you
because, you've made me happy?

436
00:44:22,940 --> 00:44:26,671
Good that Raka told me you were
here! - Oh! So he told you?

437
00:44:27,178 --> 00:44:31,512
I will not spare you, you creep!
-Wild cat!!

438
00:44:31,916 --> 00:44:34,180
You are wild cat!!

439
00:44:44,528 --> 00:44:46,860
What do you think of yourself?.
You Keep beating me every now and then

440
00:44:47,198 --> 00:44:48,756
I'll run away from home.

441
00:44:48,866 --> 00:44:51,528
I will not look for you!
Raka, go get her!

442
00:44:57,508 --> 00:45:00,909
Aunty, she has gone, what will
we do about ourwork now?

443
00:45:01,545 --> 00:45:05,140
Why you had to hit her,
she was just playing with marbles!

444
00:45:05,549 --> 00:45:07,540
Should you hit with a stick,
look at her!

445
00:45:20,564 --> 00:45:22,725
You are so big and
yet you are crying?

446
00:45:24,168 --> 00:45:26,636
What is the matter,
did someone hit you?

447
00:45:27,238 --> 00:45:32,175
Why don't you say?
- That man took my school fees!

448
00:45:32,510 --> 00:45:35,741
Oh! You have lost
your school fees in gambling?

449
00:45:36,514 --> 00:45:40,177
Why did you play?
Alright, come with me!

450
00:45:40,651 --> 00:45:43,176
Come on, bet your money!
Bet on your cards!

451
00:45:48,192 --> 00:45:53,186
Talk to me, aren't you
ashamed to dupe a child?

452
00:45:53,531 --> 00:45:55,522
I've not duped him, he has
lost that money in gambling.

453
00:45:55,733 --> 00:45:58,201
It's as good as duping,
come on, give his money back!

454
00:45:58,469 --> 00:46:02,132
What if I don't?
- I'll drag you to the police station.

455
00:46:02,306 --> 00:46:04,797
I am not scared, let me see who
has the guts to take me there!

456
00:46:05,209 --> 00:46:07,643
I can take your father there too!

457
00:46:08,813 --> 00:46:10,804
I can deal very well with
people like you.

458
00:46:11,148 --> 00:46:13,708
Stop pushing me!
- Confess in front ofhim.

459
00:46:14,251 --> 00:46:17,482
Sir, he has a gambling
den in our area.

460
00:46:17,922 --> 00:46:20,152
He even looted this poor boy's
school fees.

461
00:46:20,491 --> 00:46:24,723
What nonsense are you talking?
- Raghu, you've started again?

462
00:46:25,162 --> 00:46:28,563
I was broke, sir.
- How much money did you play for?

463
00:46:29,467 --> 00:46:33,335
Put him in the cell and take out
Rs. 20/- and give it to this child.

464
00:46:33,771 --> 00:46:37,764
If you gamble next time then
I will lock you up too!

465
00:46:38,209 --> 00:46:41,178
Out you go now and you...

466
00:46:50,187 --> 00:46:52,178
you come with me,
I want your statement!

467
00:46:52,490 --> 00:46:55,653
My statement!
- Tukaram, get me a glass of water.

468
00:46:56,193 --> 00:47:00,186
I'll give my statement but I won't
get involved in court matters.

469
00:47:00,598 --> 00:47:03,123
After all, I am
a service class girl.

470
00:47:11,609 --> 00:47:13,600
It's strange that you've come here.

471
00:47:14,478 --> 00:47:16,708
I am a very bold person.
I can go anywhere.

472
00:47:16,881 --> 00:47:19,213
Hello, is that Mr. Badrinath?

473
00:47:20,151 --> 00:47:22,483
We have found her, she is here.

474
00:47:23,154 --> 00:47:26,146
You come here quickly
within 5 minutes.

475
00:47:32,229 --> 00:47:36,757
Sir, my statement?
- I'll just have it typed.

476
00:47:37,501 --> 00:47:40,334
But tell me, why did
you go away from home?

477
00:47:40,638 --> 00:47:44,165
Actually sir, I don't like
this everyday hassle!

478
00:47:44,508 --> 00:47:46,499
That is why I left home,
now let them look for me!

479
00:47:46,844 --> 00:47:51,178
Never mind, I've called them up,
they must be on theirway.

480
00:47:51,415 --> 00:47:53,406
Who they?
-Your uncle and aunt!

481
00:47:53,651 --> 00:47:57,451
Who did you say?
-Your uncle and aunt!

482
00:47:57,721 --> 00:47:59,951
I don't have an uncle nor an aunt!

483
00:48:00,457 --> 00:48:04,450
That's bad, such small fights
cannot sever relationships!

484
00:48:04,828 --> 00:48:11,131
Don't say that, Seeta!
- Seeta?! What confusion is this?

485
00:48:11,569 --> 00:48:15,130
My name is Geeta and
I am leaving, good bye!

486
00:48:15,372 --> 00:48:17,670
Catch her, don't let her run!!

487
00:48:51,175 --> 00:48:53,166
Open the door quickly!

488
00:48:55,946 --> 00:48:57,777
What is this?

489
00:49:07,191 --> 00:49:09,182
Inspector, where is
our niece, Seeta?

490
00:49:09,460 --> 00:49:11,724
Tell us soon, where is she?

491
00:49:13,497 --> 00:49:17,194
Oh, my!
- See it for yourself!

492
00:49:22,306 --> 00:49:26,208
Come down, child!
-You come up, fatso!

493
00:49:28,212 --> 00:49:31,204
I think she has
actually become mad!

494
00:49:32,216 --> 00:49:36,380
Seeta my child, we are
your uncle and aunt!

495
00:49:36,754 --> 00:49:39,222
You look like a pair of
cartoons to me!

496
00:49:41,225 --> 00:49:47,221
We've come to take you home.
-Am I your father's property?

497
00:49:49,300 --> 00:49:54,567
Look, if you don't come down
then I'll put on the fan!

498
00:49:54,772 --> 00:49:59,232
Don't do that, I will come down!

499
00:50:05,182 --> 00:50:08,379
Uncle!...Aunty!!...

500
00:50:11,188 --> 00:50:13,179
Which oil do you use?
-What?

501
00:50:13,557 --> 00:50:19,189
Can we take her home?
- Please do that!

502
00:50:19,596 --> 00:50:21,188
Let's go now!
- Stop screaming.

503
00:50:21,332 --> 00:50:23,698
Thank you very much, inspector.

504
00:50:36,013 --> 00:50:38,709
Thank you very much!
-Will you come along now?

505
00:50:44,221 --> 00:50:45,483
Sit down!

506
00:50:49,760 --> 00:50:52,558
This car is really very good!

507
00:51:03,340 --> 00:51:06,605
Uncle, where are we going?

508
00:51:07,311 --> 00:51:10,178
We are going home.
- Home?! Whose house?

509
00:51:10,514 --> 00:51:16,180
You'll know it in sometime, I'll
thrash you on reaching home!

510
00:51:16,553 --> 00:51:18,680
Why do you keep nudging me, fatso?
-What?

511
00:51:19,189 --> 00:51:22,181
I lovingly told you, fatso!

512
00:51:22,393 --> 00:51:24,190
Did you hear that?
- Forget it, she's a child.

513
00:51:24,361 --> 00:51:27,558
I'll cut off your tongue,
did you understand?

514
00:51:27,898 --> 00:51:30,628
What nonsense is this, at the police
station you were calling me child...

515
00:51:31,201 --> 00:51:33,192
and here you are...
- Shut up!

516
00:51:42,679 --> 00:51:44,544
Oh! She's there, stop the car!!

517
00:51:45,215 --> 00:51:47,547
Go after her and catch her!

518
00:51:49,720 --> 00:51:53,212
She's is our daughter and she's mad,
we were taking her to the asylum...

519
00:51:53,557 --> 00:51:56,219
and now she has run away,
please help us to catch her!

520
00:51:56,593 --> 00:51:59,562
Please help us, hurry up!!

521
00:51:59,930 --> 00:52:01,488
What are you doing, run after her!
-You also come along!

522
00:53:04,161 --> 00:53:06,493
Oh! She jumped on the
other side, get her!

523
00:54:10,494 --> 00:54:13,486
Hey! What are you doing?
You've damaged my car!

524
00:54:17,167 --> 00:54:22,161
Come out and see what you've
done!

525
00:54:22,573 --> 00:54:25,770
Do you have a problem with your
eyes, can't you see properly?

526
00:54:26,176 --> 00:54:29,168
How could you use your brakes
suddenly? Who gave you a licence?

527
00:54:29,613 --> 00:54:32,514
Forget it, let's go!
-You keep quiet!

528
00:54:36,186 --> 00:54:39,713
He's my youngest son but what
about this bumper that you've broken?

529
00:54:40,190 --> 00:54:42,750
What do you think you were driving,
you've broken my headlights too!

530
00:54:43,193 --> 00:54:45,184
Why don't you wear glasses?

531
00:54:45,529 --> 00:54:48,191
How can you drive like this, without
giving a signal, you use the brakes?

532
00:54:49,766 --> 00:54:52,200
Hey! Talk to me!
- I can talk to anyone I feel like!

533
00:54:52,536 --> 00:54:54,527
Why did you use the brake?
- Did he use the brake of your car?

534
00:54:54,638 --> 00:54:56,799
How can you use brakes of my car,
it's not for public!

535
00:54:57,207 --> 00:54:59,198
We put brakes on our car.
- So what?

536
00:54:59,376 --> 00:55:02,641
Tell me now.
-You should've seen that I was behind

537
00:55:03,146 --> 00:55:04,773
There's nothing worth
seeing in you!

538
00:55:04,881 --> 00:55:06,849
Don't act smart!
Don't argue with me.

539
00:55:07,150 --> 00:55:09,744
We don't have eyes at the back
of our heads!

540
00:55:10,220 --> 00:55:12,211
You were behind,
you could have seen us!

541
00:55:12,489 --> 00:55:16,152
What is she saying? If there are
2-4 drivers more like you then...

542
00:55:16,493 --> 00:55:18,654
Please listen...
- Don't interrupt and annoy me!

543
00:55:19,162 --> 00:55:23,155
With people like you, we must have
2 drivers, one ahead and one behind!

544
00:55:23,667 --> 00:55:28,161
Don't talk too much
or I will slap you!

545
00:55:33,176 --> 00:55:37,442
Don't act tough with me, I'll file
a police complaint against you!

546
00:55:39,449 --> 00:55:41,576
Shirin, note down their number!

547
00:55:44,988 --> 00:55:47,548
He went away!!

548
00:55:48,625 --> 00:55:52,186
It was our fault and you
started lecturing him!

549
00:55:52,529 --> 00:55:55,191
If you get involved in a squabble,
this is the way you should talk!

550
00:55:55,532 --> 00:55:58,524
Is it so? Okay, tell me one thing...

551
00:55:59,202 --> 00:56:03,730
how did you get into this car?
- From the door, where else?

552
00:56:05,142 --> 00:56:07,474
No, I mean, where did
you sit in this car?

553
00:56:08,145 --> 00:56:10,136
On the seat, where else?

554
00:56:12,249 --> 00:56:14,149
I mean...
-What do you mean?

555
00:56:15,318 --> 00:56:17,149
Forget it.
- No, ask me!

556
00:56:19,156 --> 00:56:22,592
Okay, where are you going?
-Where are you going?

557
00:56:23,393 --> 00:56:25,691
I am going to Mahableshwar
to meet my parents.

558
00:56:26,430 --> 00:56:29,763
Does that mean half the car
will go somewhere else?

559
00:56:30,167 --> 00:56:32,499
Not at all!

560
00:56:33,170 --> 00:56:35,502
Then don't ask me, even I am
going to the same place.

561
00:56:37,174 --> 00:56:38,835
You are too much!

562
00:56:39,342 --> 00:56:42,175
That I am but you ask
too many questions!

563
00:56:51,221 --> 00:56:57,524
Great! Looks like
you are a very rich man!

564
00:56:58,195 --> 00:57:04,134
I may look but looks can be
deceptive! Even you looked different on that day!

565
00:57:05,135 --> 00:57:06,466
Which day?

566
00:57:06,803 --> 00:57:11,399
That day!
- Oh, that day! How was I looking?

567
00:57:12,142 --> 00:57:16,738
A stupid girl, trying to
pursue western fashion...

568
00:57:17,147 --> 00:57:23,575
with excessive make up on your
face!

569
00:57:24,254 --> 00:57:25,812
Me?!
-Yes, you!

570
00:57:26,823 --> 00:57:29,314
And look at you today. Do you know
how you look in these clothes?

571
00:57:29,559 --> 00:57:31,390
How?
- Like a gypsy girl!

572
00:57:31,595 --> 00:57:36,157
That I am!
- I don't know what you are!

573
00:57:37,167 --> 00:57:39,158
But I would surely
like to know you better!

574
00:57:41,171 --> 00:57:46,165
Forget all this, before my parents
come, go and change into a sari.

575
00:57:47,978 --> 00:57:49,172
Come.

576
00:57:49,446 --> 00:57:51,573
But what is wrong
with these clothes?

577
00:57:52,315 --> 00:57:54,749
They are not bad,
they are very good!

578
00:57:55,252 --> 00:57:57,743
But is it necessary that whenever
my parents see you...

579
00:57:58,188 --> 00:58:00,179
you should always be
in a fancy dress?

580
00:58:00,457 --> 00:58:02,789
It's not necessary.
- Then let's go!

581
00:58:03,126 --> 00:58:04,286
Alright!

582
00:58:07,397 --> 00:58:09,592
This is my sister, Nirmala's room.

583
00:58:10,133 --> 00:58:12,124
She is married and lives in Germany.

584
00:58:12,602 --> 00:58:16,129
There are few saris in this, you
can choose anyone from them!

585
00:58:16,473 --> 00:58:18,236
I'll wear it right away!

586
00:58:49,506 --> 00:58:57,504
You are supposed to tie them on
your feet and then walk with them!

587
00:58:58,782 --> 00:59:00,682
Oh, I see!

588
00:59:03,520 --> 00:59:06,182
I think my parents have come,
you get dressed quickly...

589
00:59:06,456 --> 00:59:08,185
I'll go down.

590
00:59:20,203 --> 00:59:23,661
Son, the gardener said that
some girl has come with you.

591
00:59:24,207 --> 00:59:29,645
Girl?! Oh, I met Seeta on the way
and I got her...

592
00:59:30,213 --> 00:59:32,204
You got her here, what was the
need?

593
00:59:33,550 --> 00:59:37,680
Seeta is very different from
what we thought about her!

594
00:59:37,921 --> 00:59:39,548
What about the scene
we saw the other day?

595
00:59:39,656 --> 00:59:41,647
It was just a drama.

596
00:59:42,225 --> 00:59:44,887
Yes mother, I was shocked
to see her today.

597
00:59:46,897 --> 00:59:49,695
Mother, she is a very smart
and a nice girl!

598
00:59:56,239 --> 00:59:59,402
Unless you don't see her,
you will not believe me!

599
01:00:00,243 --> 01:00:02,438
You wait here, I'll just get her.

600
01:00:05,882 --> 01:00:07,509
Are you ready?...

601
01:00:30,206 --> 01:00:33,198
You tie it on your feet
and then walk!

602
01:00:34,210 --> 01:00:36,735
And then you slip and fall?
- Sometimes.

603
01:00:37,681 --> 01:00:39,876
Won't you meet my parents?
-Yes, I will.

604
01:00:40,216 --> 01:00:41,513
Then let's go.
- Come on.

605
01:00:41,618 --> 01:00:43,210
Just a minute!

606
01:00:49,326 --> 01:00:51,226
Shall we go?
- Oh, yes!

607
01:00:53,430 --> 01:00:55,421
Aren't you an Indian girl?
-Yes, I am!

608
01:00:55,665 --> 01:00:59,726
Then you are supposed to act
coy in front of my parents.

609
01:01:00,236 --> 01:01:01,828
I understand.
- So come on, act coy!

610
01:01:01,938 --> 01:01:04,168
Let's go there then I'll act coy.
-Alright.

611
01:01:15,852 --> 01:01:17,683
That's a bit too much!

612
01:01:18,855 --> 01:01:21,187
That's fine, let's go.

613
01:01:22,859 --> 01:01:27,193
What will I have to do there?
- Nothing, shake hands with them.

614
01:01:27,430 --> 01:01:29,364
What?
- I am sorry...

615
01:01:29,532 --> 01:01:31,193
I said it wrong, just seek blessings.
-Your blessings?!

616
01:01:31,301 --> 01:01:33,292
No, my parent's blessings.

617
01:01:36,272 --> 01:01:38,263
And then yours?
-We'll see that later.

618
01:01:40,877 --> 01:01:44,210
You already know her!
- Come children, sit down.

619
01:01:47,217 --> 01:01:49,208
You'll sit.
-Yes, please sit.

620
01:02:12,609 --> 01:02:14,338
Seek their blessings!

621
01:02:19,349 --> 01:02:24,184
Is everyone fine?
- Oh, yes!

622
01:02:24,521 --> 01:02:27,183
I liked everyone, you all!

623
01:02:27,757 --> 01:02:31,750
I am not talking about us,
how are your uncle and aunt?

624
01:02:32,262 --> 01:02:36,198
Oh, my! This aunt has come here
too! Well they...

625
01:02:36,466 --> 01:02:40,459
Child, don't they behave
properly with you?

626
01:02:40,770 --> 01:02:44,638
In front of everyone she dotes on
me and puts up an act of love...

627
01:02:45,208 --> 01:02:47,540
but when we are alone,
she acts like a demon!

628
01:02:51,214 --> 01:02:53,205
Mother, I had a doubt
on that day itself.

629
01:02:53,583 --> 01:02:58,213
I had seen it myself that
the other girl Sheila, kicked her!

630
01:02:58,555 --> 01:03:02,150
Didn't she kick you?
Don't lie now!

631
01:03:02,926 --> 01:03:08,523
Why should I lie?
Yes, she did kick me.

632
01:03:09,165 --> 01:03:14,159
That means the other day
what we saw was just an act!

633
01:03:14,404 --> 01:03:18,602
I have to put up an act everyday,
tell me what else can I do?

634
01:03:19,175 --> 01:03:21,405
I have to do all these things
to satiate my hunger.

635
01:03:21,678 --> 01:03:25,671
Why do you need to do that?
You don't live on their mercy!

636
01:03:26,182 --> 01:03:29,174
I have started
detesting those people!

637
01:03:29,686 --> 01:03:35,181
That day they presented her in such
a weird manner and look at her today!

638
01:03:35,859 --> 01:03:38,191
I always look good
in borrowed clothes!

639
01:03:42,198 --> 01:03:44,189
We like her frankness!

640
01:03:45,201 --> 01:03:49,194
Child, where are your bags?
- Bags?!

641
01:03:51,641 --> 01:03:58,205
Oh yes, her bags! Well actually,
her bags were left behind.

642
01:03:58,548 --> 01:04:01,142
And she came with me!

643
01:04:03,186 --> 01:04:05,746
Child, you must have
informed at home, isn't it?

644
01:04:06,156 --> 01:04:10,149
Oh, my! In this chaos I forgot
that I do have a family!

645
01:04:13,196 --> 01:04:17,155
God, I have nobody in
this world who loves me...

646
01:04:18,234 --> 01:04:23,171
it's said that you love the people
who are not loved by anyone!

647
01:04:24,574 --> 01:04:27,839
I am coming to seek your refuge.

648
01:04:33,449 --> 01:04:36,714
Wow! That was a brilliant jump!

649
01:04:41,191 --> 01:04:44,183
Chief, that person is drowning!

650
01:04:51,968 --> 01:04:55,529
Aunty!!

651
01:04:58,241 --> 01:05:00,709
What happened to Geeta?
- Raka is getting her.

652
01:05:01,144 --> 01:05:03,135
She jumped in the river
to commit suicide.

653
01:05:21,464 --> 01:05:26,595
Geeta, my child, please get up!
Why isn't she talking?

654
01:05:31,174 --> 01:05:34,166
Where...
- Don't worry, child!

655
01:05:34,611 --> 01:05:39,742
You are perfectly alright!
-Why did you save me?

656
01:05:40,183 --> 01:05:44,677
Don't say that, child. Nobody ends
life over such a petty fight.

657
01:05:45,421 --> 01:05:48,754
I did not know that a small joke
would lead to such a serious thing.

658
01:05:49,626 --> 01:05:51,355
She's alright now.

659
01:05:52,195 --> 01:05:54,527
What is all this? Who are you?

660
01:05:54,831 --> 01:05:57,527
What is the matterwith you?
I am your mother, Geeta!

661
01:05:58,635 --> 01:06:00,796
Geeta? I am Seeta!

662
01:06:01,204 --> 01:06:03,468
Oh God, what is wrong
with my daughter?

663
01:06:04,140 --> 01:06:09,134
My child, don't worry, nobody
will scream at you anymore!

664
01:06:10,146 --> 01:06:14,139
I will always love you, come close!

665
01:06:15,151 --> 01:06:18,143
Will you ever leave your mother
now?

666
01:06:19,155 --> 01:06:22,147
Mother!
- Stop crying, child!

667
01:06:24,160 --> 01:06:25,149
Mother!!

668
01:06:31,467 --> 01:06:32,661
Oh, my God!

669
01:06:32,835 --> 01:06:37,169
If you hurry up then you'll
surely break your bones.

670
01:06:37,473 --> 01:06:40,772
Let it break, you are
a doctor, you can fix it!

671
01:06:41,611 --> 01:06:44,171
You can tie that white cloth
on it, what is that called?

672
01:06:44,914 --> 01:06:46,848
White cloth?!
Oh, you mean a plaster?

673
01:06:49,185 --> 01:06:50,846
No, it's called a plaster!

674
01:06:54,857 --> 01:06:58,190
Never mind, forget it! If you
really want to learn skating...

675
01:06:58,528 --> 01:07:03,465
then listen to me carefully, keep
yourweight on the front wheels...

676
01:07:04,133 --> 01:07:05,395
like this, do you understand.

677
01:07:05,501 --> 01:07:08,493
What you do is keep yourweight on
the rearwheels and that is why...

678
01:07:16,145 --> 01:07:20,138
Doctor, if you want to learn skating
then remember one thing...

679
01:07:21,818 --> 01:07:24,685
don't keep yourweight on rear
wheels, keep it on the front wheels!

680
01:07:25,321 --> 01:07:26,618
Like this!!...

681
