''Watch it... let's go hand in hand''

687
01:08:40,530 --> 01:08:42,691
''Let's move, O companion...''

688
01:08:43,232 --> 01:08:47,566
''Walk with me...
all day and night, like this''

689
01:08:48,171 --> 01:08:52,505
''With your hand in mine...
let's steady ourselves and go along''

690
01:08:58,815 --> 01:09:02,581
''The weather's so lovely,
