691
01:09:08,858 --> 01:09:12,191
''The weather's so lovely
as it is...''

692
01:09:13,796 --> 01:09:17,527
''and we're also crazy at heart''

693
01:09:18,201 --> 01:09:22,535
''Mind the mountains.
Don't collide with them...''

694
01:09:23,206 --> 01:09:27,802
''like a cloud...
let's move, my love''

695
01:09:56,239 --> 01:09:59,902
''Let the world laugh,
