01:10:06,249 --> 01:10:10,185
''Let the world laugh,
ifit wilI''

697
01:10:11,187 --> 01:10:15,180
''Let the kick of
the weather get to us''

698
01:10:15,625 --> 01:10:20,187
''Let me live in your eyes...''

